The paper discusses deep neural networks and their challenges in training and generalization, which are common topics in the machine learning community. The proposed approach is based on systems of ordinary differential equations, which is a topic in the field of numerical analysis and dynamical systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also discusses applications in image classification (cs.CV) and nonlinear dynamical systems (cs.AI), which are additional possible categories.
